  <name>COSMIC Camera</name>
  <summary>Capture photos and videos</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      COSMIC Camera is a modern, easy-to-use camera application designed for the COSMIC desktop.
      Whether you need to snap a quick photo or record a video, COSMIC Camera provides a clean
      and intuitive interface that stays out of your way.
    </p>
    <p>
      Built with simplicity in mind, the app automatically detects your cameras and microphones
      via PipeWire, letting you start capturing moments right away. When you need more control,
      the settings panel gives you access to resolution, frame rate, and encoding options.
    </p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Take photos and record videos with audio</li>
      <li>Real-time preview filters to add creative effects</li>
      <li>Hardware-accelerated video encoding (VA-API, NVENC, QuickSync)</li>
      <li>Support for multiple cameras and audio devices</li>
      <li>Adjustable resolution, frame rate, and bitrate quality</li>
      <li>Theatre mode for distraction-free fullscreen preview</li>
      <li>Built-in gallery to quickly view your captures</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

